description:
- Chocolate Donut Backpack "A soft backpack in the shape of a donut."
 - Chocolate Donut Beret "A soft beret in the shape of a donut."
 - Chocolate Donut Hat "A plush donut that can be worn on the head."
*You can buy it at any time in the game shop( Fashion Store in Castle St. ) when you purchase it. 
 - Chocolate Donut Wreath "[Wall] A tasty-looking donut wall decoration. (Not for consumption)"
 - Chocolate Donut Basket "[Tabletop] A tasty-looking donut ornament. (Not for consumption)"
 - Donut Assortment Basket "[Tabletop] A tasty-looking donut ornament. (Not for consumption)"
*You can buy it at any time in the game shop( General Store in Yano Market ) when you purchase it.
name: Chocolate Donut Fair
